snippet.title: FULL FIGHT HIGHLIGHTS | Manny Pacquiao vs Mario Barrios | Prime Video PPV
snippet.description:
Hall of Fame boxing legend Manny “Pacman” Pacquiao returned to battle WBC Welterweight World Champion Mario “El Azteca” Barrios in a main event showdown headlining a star-studded PBC Pay-Per-View event on Prime Video from the MGM Grand Garden Arena in Las Vegas.

» Subscribe to Sports on Prime: https://www.youtube.com/@SportsonPrime?sub_confirmation=1 

*ABOUT PACQUIAO VS. BARRIOS*

Pacquiao vs. Barrios will see Hall of Fame boxing legend Manny “Pacman” Pacquiao and WBC Welterweight World Champion Mario “El Azteca” Barrios square off in the main event of a star-studded PBC Pay-Per-View event on Prime Video on Saturday, July 19 from the MGM Grand Garden Arena in Las Vegas.

In the co-main event, WBC Super Welterweight World Champion Sebastian “The Towering Inferno” Fundora and Australian superstar Tim Tszyu will rematch after engaging in 2024’s bloodiest fight.

The action will also feature Mexican star Isaac “Pitbull” Cruz, facing all-action contender Omar Salcido in a 10-round super lightweight showdown. Cruz was originally scheduled to face Angel Fierro, who was forced to withdraw due to a medical emergency. Plus former two-division world champion Brandon “The Heartbreaker” Figueroa and top contender Joet Gonzalez kick off the pay-per-view at 8 p.m. ET/5 p.m. PT with a 10-round featherweight showdown.

About Prime Video:
Prime Video supports a growing lineup of live sports globally, including Thursday Night Football, the WNBA, the Seattle Storm, the New York Yankees, Overtime Elite, and the Professional Pickleball Association in the United States; ONE Championship and NWSL in the United States and Canada; Premier League in the United Kingdom; ATP and WTA tennis in the United Kingdom and Ireland; UEFA Champions League football in Germany and Italy; Roland-Garros and Ligue 1 in France; Australian swimming globally; New Zealand Cricket in India; as well as Copa do Brasil football and the NBA in Brazil; and boxing and the 2023 World Baseball Classic in Japan. While availability varies by marketplace, fans can also subscribe to streaming services such as Eurosport, FOX Sports (Mexico), Viaplay Sport, MLB.TV, NBA League Pass, NBA TV, DAZN (Germany and Spain), and Premiere FC (Brazil) through Prime Video Channels. snippet.title: CJ7 (2008) | This boy obtained Iron Man's equipment. 🦾💥👽🛸
snippet.description:
🛸【CJ7 | What if the poorest kid met an alien pet?】
#CJ7 #StephenChow #HeartwarmingSciFi #AlienDog #SingleDad #Tearjerker 💔🧒👨‍🔧👽🐾✨

👨‍🔧 He's a construction worker who can barely afford a steamed bun for his son.
🧒 His son goes to a fancy school… where he's bullied every day.
They live in poverty. No toys, no gadgets—just each other.
Until one day…
a mysterious alien orb crashes into their world 🌠

🛸 That orb becomes CJ7 — a squishy, glowing alien pet
who can fix broken things, float in the air, and bring junk toys to life 🎮⚙️✨
For the first time, the boy smiles, laughs, and feels seen.
He thinks he found a pet,
but he’s really found a miracle friend.

💥 CJ7 can fix everything—except real life.
When his dad collapses from exhaustion…
there’s no alien magic that can save him.
Not this time. Not even CJ7 can stop what's coming…

🐾 But maybe—just maybe—what he left behind,
is enough to teach the boy how to stand up again.

🎬 CJ7 isn’t just a sci-fi kids movie.
It’s Stephen Chow’s most emotional story.
A love letter to all single parents.
A fable about dreams, loss… and never giving up.

👨‍👦 "You gave me nothing... except the entire universe."
😭🛸🐾💚

snippet.title: ANTBOY” (2013) | "He inherited the power of ants."🧬🐜💥
snippet.description:
🐜💥 "He was invisible… Until he got bit."
He’s not cool. Not strong. Not popular.
Just a lonely kid… with comic books, a bike, and a dream. 🚲📚
But when a bite from a genetically enhanced ant 🧬🐜 changes everything…
A hero is born.

🧬 Super strength.
🧗‍♂️ Wall-climbing.
⚡ Acid spit(?!).
He doesn’t know how it works — he just knows it does.

💬 “Call me... Antboy.”

But becoming a superhero isn’t as easy as wearing a mask.
Because in the shadows of Middelund…
👹 The Flea is watching.
A monstrous villain with his own powers.
His plan?
Crush the kid.
Unleash chaos.
And prove that heroes… don't belong.

But Antboy won’t run.
Not when his best friend is counting on him.
Not when the girl he likes is in danger.
Not when the city needs a symbol. 💪🏙️

Behind the goggles is just a boy.
But under pressure?
He becomes something more.
Not a perfect hero.
But a real one. 🐜🦸‍♂️

🔥 From Denmark's breakout superhero story, Antboy blends action and heart — with all the awkward charm of growing up and saving the world at the same time.

When responsibility crawls into your life, will you squash it?
Or rise with it?

🎬🐜 “ANTBOY” (2013) — The underdog hero you didn’t expect…
But the one we all needed.

snippet.title: 😢😢SquidGame S3| We are not horses. We are humans. #squidgame #netflix #shrots #sad
snippet.description:
Squid Game: A Gripping Tale of Desperation and Survival 😱
In a world where debt and despair crush lives, hundreds of cash-strapped contestants receive a mysterious invitation to compete in children’s games for a massive cash prize 💰—but little do they know, losing means death 💀!
Leading the pack is Seong Gi-hun, a divorced gambler drowning in debt, who joins the games hoping to win enough money to save his daughter and mother 😢.
Among the 456 players, we meet Kang Sae-byeok, a North Korean defector desperate to reunite her family 🇰🇵→🇰🇷; Cho Sang-woo, Gi-hun’s childhood friend and a disgraced businessman on the run from the law 🕵️♂️; and Abdul Ali, a kind Pakistani migrant worker trying to support his family 👨👩👧👦.
The games kick off with “Red Light, Green Light” 🚦—a simple game where players must freeze when a giant doll sings “red light”… or get shot dead on the spot 💥! Panic erupts as bodies pile up, and the survivors realize this is no ordinary contest 😰.
Next comes “Dalgona,” where players must carve a shape (circle, triangle, star, umbrella) out of a honeycomb candy without breaking it 🍯—fail, and a masked guard will shoot you 🎯! Tensions rise as contestants cheat, beg, and even betray each other to survive 😠.
Then there’s “Tug of War” 🪢, a brutal test of strength where teams of 10 fight to pull the rope—losers plummet to their deaths from a high platform 📉! Friendships are forged and shattered here, as players must choose allies wisely or face annihilation 🤝→💔.
“Marbles” is next 🎲, a game where players pair up and bet their marbles—whoever loses all their marbles loses their life 😭. This round exposes raw emotions: Gi-hun lies to an elderly friend to survive, while Ali is betrayed by Sang-woo in a heart-wrenching twist 😭💔.
After a chaotic riot and a vote to end the games (which fails), the survivors return for “Glass Stepping Stones” 🔍—a bridge where each step is either tempered glass (safe) or regular glass (shatters, sending you falling to your death) 😱! Players must guess correctly or die, leading to more tragic losses 😭.
The final game is the namesake “Squid Game” 🦑, a childhood playground game where Gi-hun and Sang-woo face off in a brutal battle for the 45.6 billion won prize 🏆. As they fight, flashbacks reveal Sang-woo’s descent into greed and Gi-hun’s struggle to hold onto his humanity 🥺.
In the end, only one player walks away with the money… but victory comes at a terrible cost, leaving them haunted by the horrors they witnessed and committed 😔.
Who will survive? And is the prize worth losing your soul? 🤔 The answer will keep you on the edge of your seat until the very last second ⏳!
